{"tid":353633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【圖】如何有創意及有效地舉報拒載的士狗","createTime":"2017-08-09T17:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T18:33:36.000Z","uid":68060,"like":91,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b34193ed08283f541dc215626b04816eb3fe5d6","tid":353633,"uid":68060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T17:56:05.000Z","msg":"夜闌人靜係元朗工業區截的士難過叫肥菜找數<br />\n十架的士九架都拒載<br />\n<br />\n再係咁落去唔係辦法<br />\n<br />\n所以我截的士前都開著部Digital Video(即DV) 影住每架路過嘅的士<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/015217_220b57cda85357a5c712b0d414f5a3f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F015217_220b57cda85357a5c712b0d414f5a3f7.jpg&h=5c067a92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次拒載的士狗KG9383 已經比我捉到無冚祺拒載<br />\n（稍後有片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/015325_1b8ae0821e43d8fc825b21ef68fd051d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F015325_1b8ae0821e43d8fc825b21ef68fd051d.jpg&h=c8ef0020&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24eb2f594f09e84d44ef7536e4d64ee1bb9133fb","tid":353633,"uid":68060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T18:12:37.000Z","msg":"1823見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b275c7f009d3f50bcabbd45114dd562be9183437","tid":353633,"uid":322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T01:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341c81d4adfcdf6a9ee76530c5c324bf8443fba9","tid":353633,"uid":107784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T01:07:16.000Z","msg":"ching good ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8315dbc8b1c5246ea13c85462866bc43faae9d79","tid":353633,"uid":85591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T01:07:22.000Z","msg":"的士狗有